videos.description: Ryan Woolridge hustles to steal a pass on defense and finishes with a double-clutch layup in traffic at the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Woolridge steals and scores for Gonzaga) 2019/12/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Woolridge steals and scores for Gonzaga

videos.description: Jaden McDaniels gets a pass in the corner, drives baseline and rises up for a thunderous tomahawk slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McDaniels flushes powerful baseline jam) 2019/12/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDaniels flushes powerful baseline jam

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Joel Ayayi knocks down a deep 3-pointer to put Gonzaga ahead by six in the final minute.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gonzaga's Ayayi sinks dagger triple from way downtown) 2019/12/08

videos.headline: Gonzaga's Ayayi sinks dagger triple from way downtown
